&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re in an unbelievably exciting area of tech and are fundamentally reshaping the data storage industry. Here, you lead with innovative thinking, grow along with us, and join the smartest team in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This type of work—work that changes the world—is what the tech industry was founded on. So, if you&#39;re ready to seize the endless opportunities and leave your mark, come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everpure（旧 Pure Storage）では、日本市場におけるさらなる事業成長の実現に向けて、国内の大手システムインテグレーター（SIer）および販売パートナーとのビジネス拡大をリードいただくパートナーアカウントマネージャー（PAM）を募集しています。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本ポジションは、パートナーテクニカルマネージャー（PTM）と連携しながら、担当パートナーとの中長期的な関係構築と事業成長を推進する重要な役割です。営業、技術、マーケティング、サポート、チャネル部門など社内の各チームと密接に連携し、パートナー企業との協業を通じて市場でのビジネス拡大を実現していただきます。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;職務内容&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;パートナー戦略の立案およびビジネス拡大の推進&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;担当する大手SIer・販売パートナーと中長期的な成長戦略を策定し、共同ビジネスの拡大を推進します。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;パートナーの事業戦略や市場動向、業界トレンドを踏まえたビジネス機会の発掘&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Everpureのグローバルおよびリージョナル戦略と連動した成長計画の策定&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;具体的なアクションプランの立案・実行および成果創出&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;売上拡大に向けた継続的なパートナービジネスの推進&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;パートナーとの関係強化および協業促進&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;パートナー企業の営業部門・技術部門との信頼関係を構築し、Everpure製品およびソリューションの価値を浸透させます。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;パートナー担当者との継続的なリレーション構築&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;提案活動や案件創出に向けた協業推進&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;製品・ソリューションに関するイネーブルメント活動の実施&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;パートナー内におけるEverpureの認知度・優先度向上&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;エグゼクティブレベルでの関係構築&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;パートナー企業の経営層や事業責任者との関係を構築し、戦略的な協業を推進します。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;経営層との定期的なコミュニケーションの実施&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;両社のビジネス目標に基づく協業施策の推進&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;パートナー企業におけるEverpureの主要な窓口としての役割遂行&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;パートナー運営の最適化&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;パートナー企業とEverpure双方の業務プロセスを理解し、より効率的で効果的な協業体制の構築を目指します。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;パートナーとの協業プロセスにおける課題の特定と改善提案&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;社内外の関係部門との調整および連携強化&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;パートナーエクスペリエンス向上に向けた施策の立案・実行&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;応募資格&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;必須要件&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;パートナーとの協業を通じて事業成長を実現してきた経験&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SIer、販売代理店、またはチャネルビジネスにおける営業・アライアンス・パートナー管理経験&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;戦略的な視点を持ち、自らビジネス機会を創出・推進できる方&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;社内外の多様なステークホルダーを巻き込みながら業務を推進できる高いコミュニケーション能力&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;日本語ネイティブレベル&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;歓迎要件&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;英語によるコミュニケーション能力（ビジネスレベル歓迎）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;エンタープライズIT業界での営業またはパートナー管理経験&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ストレージ、インフラ、クラウド、データプラットフォーム領域に関する知識・経験&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;このポジションの魅力&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;日本市場の成長を牽引する中核ポジション&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everpureの日本市場における成長戦略の中心となり、大手パートナーとの協業を通じて大きなビジネスインパクトを創出できます。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;経営層との接点&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;パートナー企業およびEverpure双方のCxO・VPクラスとの対話を通じて、ビジネス戦略レベルでの経験を積むことができます。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;グローバルな環境&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;海外チームとの連携機会も多く、多様なバックグラウンドを持つメンバーと協働しながら経験の幅を広げることができます。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;リーダーシップを発揮できる環境&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;直属の部下の有無に関わらず、社内外の関係者を巻き込みながら成果を生み出すリーダーシップを発揮していただけます。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;キャリア成長の機会&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;実績や成果に応じて、より広範なパートナー戦略を担うポジションや、組織マネジメントを担うPeople Managerへのキャリアパスも期待できます。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU CAN EXPECT FROM US:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Innovation&lt;/strong&gt;: We celebrate those who think critically, like a challenge, and aspire to be trailblazers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Growth&lt;/strong&gt;: We give you the space and support to grow along with us and to contribute to something meaningful. We have been named Fortune&#39;s Best Workplaces in Technology™, Fortune&#39;s Best Workplaces in the Bay Area™, and certified as a Great Place to Work®!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team&lt;/strong&gt;: We build each other up and set aside ego for the greater good.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&l

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re in an unbelievably exciting area of tech and are fundamentally reshaping the data storage industry. Here, you lead with innovative thinking, grow along with us, and join the smartest team in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This type of work—work that changes the world—is what the tech industry was founded on. So, if you&#39;re ready to seize the endless opportunities and leave your mark, come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everpure is looking to hire a Global Systems Integrator Senior Account Director to support the NTT DATA global account across EMEA &amp;amp; LATAM.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a senior-level business development, sales execution and regional partner leadership role, based in Europe, with responsibility for driving Everpure’s growth with NTT DATA across all relevant business units, countries and routes to market in EMEA &amp;amp; LATAM.&amp;nbsp;The GSI business is a key growth engine for Everpure, and NTT DATA is one of Everpure’s most strategically important global partners. This role will work directly with the Global Account Director for NTT DATA, regional Everpure sales teams, partner teams, technical leaders and NTT DATA stakeholders to translate the global account strategy into measurable regional execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The primary responsibility will be to execute the NTT DATA account strategy across EMEA &amp;amp; LATAM, developing qualified pipeline, supporting strategic pursuits, driving deals to close, and building repeatable sales motions across NTT DATA Technology Solutions, Cloud &amp;amp; Security, managed services, country entities and strategic customer engagements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Senior Account Executive will be responsible for creating and managing detailed account, stakeholder and closure plans, contributing to the global and regional account plans, and ensuring that EMEA &amp;amp; LATAM execution is aligned to Everpure’s broader NTT DATA growth strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate should ideally have existing relationships within NTT DATA, broad IT industry experience, strong commercial negotiation skills, and a high degree of business acumen.&amp;nbsp; They must be comfortable operating across a complex matrix of stakeholders, routes to market and countries, while maintaining a strong focus on revenue, pipeline creation and sales execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Everpure’s EMEA &amp;amp; LATAM relationship with NTT DATA for strategic sales partnering, field execution and regional growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execution of the NTT DATA global account strategy across EMEA &amp;amp; LATAM, ensuring that regional activity supports the wider Global GAM plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage account plans, stakeholder maps, pursuit plans and close plans across multiple NTT DATA entities and countries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish yourself as the go-to regional resource for NTT DATA customer-facing engagements, business development opportunities and field alignment across EMEA &amp;amp; LATAM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive qualified pipeline creation and deal progression with NTT DATA, working in partnership with Everpure end-user account teams and regional leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Everpure’s strategic growth priorities with NTT DATA, including resale growth, managed services, Portworx, modern applications, cloud, cyber resilience, AI data services and consumption-led commercial models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and coordinate joint demand generation activities with NTT DATA and Everpure, ensuring activity is targeted, measurable and connected to pipeline outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong relationships across NTT DATA executive teams, sales leadership, technical leadership, delivery, pre-sales, alliances, country teams an

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re in an unbelievably exciting area of tech and are fundamentally reshaping the data storage industry. Here, you lead with innovative thinking, grow along with us, and join the smartest team in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This type of work—work that changes the world—is what the tech industry was founded on. So, if you&#39;re ready to seize the endless opportunities and leave your mark, come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Everpure India&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is seeking a dynamic and driven&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Hunter&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;to join our &lt;strong&gt;BFSI&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Enterprise&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;team in Mumbai. In this role, you’ll be at the forefront of developing new business, working with our channel resellers and key customer accounts. Collaborate with Sales, Pre-sales, Partner sales, and Field Marketing teams to drive success in the Enterprise private sector.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Account Executive, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Promote Innovative Solutions&lt;/strong&gt;: Advocate for our all-flash enterprise storage technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build Relationships:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Foster strong connections with customers, ensuring high satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead and Strategize:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Direct pursuit teams and develop account plans to secure new customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage Sales Pipeline:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Drive activities to meet and exceed sales quotas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate with Partners:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Work with Channel, GSI, and Ecosystem Partners to position Everpure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execute Account Strategies:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Develop and implement strategies to close deals consistently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deliver Results:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Surpass quotas, maintain a strong pipeline, and drive referenceable business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicate Effectively:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Present proposals highlighting Everpure’s benefits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;WHAT YOU BRING&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To excel in this role, you should have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Passion:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;A strong drive for sales and relationship building.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enterprise Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Selling and exceeding objectives in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;BFSI&lt;/strong&gt; Enterprise Storage segment in Mumbai, India.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner Collaboration:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Experience working with Channel, GSI, and Ecosystem Partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prospecting Skills:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Advanced skills in engaging new customers required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ambition and Drive:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;A goal-oriented attitude and desire to drive change.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Proven Success:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;A track record of exceeding quotas and maintaining a robust pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adaptability:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Ability to thrive in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry Knowledge:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Understanding of cloud computing and Data Centre Architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Excellent time management and communication abilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;8+ years of field sales experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Language Skills:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Native/Bilingual French and professional English proficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#LI-ONSITE&

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re in an unbelievably exciting area of tech and are fundamentally reshaping the data storage industry. Here, you lead with innovative thinking, grow along with us, and join the smartest team in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This type of work—work that changes the world—is what the tech industry was founded on. So, if you&#39;re ready to seize the endless opportunities and leave your mark, come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everpure Germany is seeking a dynamic and driven sales person to join our&amp;nbsp;Commercial team in the Munich region. In this role, you’ll be at the forefront of developing new business, working with our channel resellers and key customer accounts. Collaborate with Sales, Pre-sales, Partner sales, and Field Marketing teams to drive success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be collaborating closely with a network of Channel, GSI and Eco-System Partners to successfully position and sell the Pure Storage platform in your assigned accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and execute account strategies and coordinate team selling efforts with partners to accurately forecast and close business on a monthly, quarterly and annual basis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver results, exceeding annual quotas, driving referenceable business and building consistent pipeline through effective prospecting and marketing initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and present comprehensive proposals to customers, articulating the business outcomes and making our customers happy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be Pure&#39;s advocate, cheerleader and spokesperson and always make sure for Pure to be our customers &amp;amp; partners first choice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate and contribute with teams internally, share knowledge and best practices with team members, contribute to internal projects and initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BRING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for customer success; through the entire sales cycle with an emphasis on post-sales customer success and satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A good listener and confident speaker with a smile on your face when doing what you love, as well as a heart of gold with a strong affinity to the colour orange🍊.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You cooperate and network effectively, creating genuine and trustful relationships with diverse people.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a self-motivated learner, showing self-awareness and demonstrating openness and curiosity. You experiment and learn from mistakes and past experiences, always showing courage and stepping out of your comfort zone. You support the development of a learning culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You anticipate, think and dream big, demonstrating a high level of aspiration. You are self-driven and show proactivity, especially when seeing problems as challenges and turning them into opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working closely with a network of Channel, GSI and Eco-System Partners to successfully position, market and sell the Pure Storage platform in your assigned accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record in delivering results; exceeding annual quotas, driving business and building consistent pipelines through effective prospecting and marketing initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A competitive attitude, a desire to disrupt the status quo, drive change and evangelize new technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to thrive in a fast-paced environment is key, a blend of large company and startup experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with Salesforce.com and Microsoft Office.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 7 years of selling experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business fluent German and English speaker.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#LI-ONSITE&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re in an unbelievably exciting area of tech and are fundamentally reshaping the data storage industry. Here, you lead with innovative thinking, grow along with us, and join the smartest team in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This type of work—work that changes the world—is what the tech industry was founded on. So, if you&#39;re ready to seize the endless opportunities and leave your mark, come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everpure is seeking an Account Executive with experience selling into customers in &lt;strong&gt;Ohio&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp; This Account Executive will coordinate the overall strategy and relationship between the assigned accounts and Everpure. They will be responsible for team-selling efforts with other teammates and strategic partners around the globe to close business on a quarterly and annual basis. The ideal candidate will currently be selling and living in the &lt;strong&gt;Greater Cleveland&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evangelize our radically simple, all-flash enterprise storage technology and data solutions, ensuring customers fully grasp Pure’s total value proposition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and invest in relationships with customers to establish Pure’s value, continually driving the highest customer satisfaction ratings in the industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead pursuit teams and develop account plans to make sure all internal resources are engaged to execute and win new Pure Customers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive and manage a healthy and robust pipeline of sales activity to assure quarterly and annual quotas are met or exceeded&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU BRING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Authenticity and a genuine desire to engage customers and understand their business challenges&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thought leadership, creativity and a Challenger Mindset; the ability to apply your customer insights and expertise in technology solutions to position Pure’s portfolio to solve persistent problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Avid hunter with proven prospecting skills, consistently opening doors to new customers and navigating seamlessly between the boardroom and the data center while passionately positioning the advantages of a Everpure solution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent interpersonal skills including written and oral communication, able to build relationships easily and deepen them over time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to assess, plan, and actively manage a territory to achieve maximum revenue and efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise leading a complex sales process with multiple stakeholders, while fostering teamwork and shared ownership internally and with Partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistent track record of exceeding quota and driving referenceable business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about post-sales customer success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8 + years of outside sales with a focus on new logo acquisition or business development; consistently delivering $5-$10M per year in revenues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Salary ranges are determined based on role, level and location. For positions open to candidates in multiple geographical locations, the base salary range is reflective of the labor market across the applicable locations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This role may be eligible for incentive pay and/or equity.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;There is no application deadline and we accept applications on an ongoing basis until the job is filled.&lt;/em&gt;&l

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re in an unbelievably exciting area of tech and are fundamentally reshaping the data storage industry. Here, you lead with innovative thinking, grow along with us, and join the smartest team in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This type of work—work that changes the world—is what the tech industry was founded on. So, if you&#39;re ready to seize the endless opportunities and leave your mark, come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everpure Data Intelligence (formerly 1touch.io) enables enterprises to discover, classify, and understand data across cloud, on-premises, and edge environments to improve AI accuracy, build trust in AI outcomes, reduce risk, and deliver measurable business impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a skilled and dynamic&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; who is driven, hard working and adaptable. In this role, you will help us land customers, primarily through outbound efforts and handling the entire sales cycle from prospecting to close.&amp;nbsp; We are building a world-class, high performance team focused on improving our customer’s business to grow our own and are in a key inflection point of revenue growth and scalability with a large opportunity to make an impact and join an early sales organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have experience targeting Fortune 500 franchise accounts + commercial (1,000-10,000 employee organizations) for use of a data discovery and classification platform and you thrive on making a quantifiable value difference in your accounts and building long-term relationships, this is the position for you!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role can be based anywhere in the U.S.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
