&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner closely with Everpure’s Scale AI and Enterprise Sales and SE teams to map accounts and close complex, large-scale deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market Intelligence:&lt;/strong&gt; Stay ahead of the curve on AI frameworks (PyTorch, TensorFlow), GPU-accelerated computing, and the competitive landscape to keep Everpure as the partner of choice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU BRING:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 7+ years of experience in Channel Management or Sales within the enterprise storage, networking, or AI infrastructure industries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Domain Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; A proven track record of selling into the AI, Deep Learning, or HPC markets. You should understand the nuances of the AI data pipeline (Ingest, Clean, Train, Inference).&lt;/li&gt;
